# FastAPI Contacts Server

This is a FastAPI server that provides a simple API for managing contacts (users) using a MySQL database.

## General Description

The server exposes 4 endpoints and works with a MySQL database.  
Each component runs in a separate Docker container.

FastAPI runs locally on port 8000  
MySQL runs locally on port 3306

---

## Endpoints

1. GET  
   http://localhost:8000/contacts  
   Returns a list of all users

2. POST  
   http://localhost:8000/contacts  
   Creates a new user

3. DELETE  
   http://localhost:8000/contacts/{id}  
   Deletes a user by id

4. UPDATE  
   http://localhost:8000/contacts/{id}  
   Updates a user by id

---

## User Structure (Input)

When creating a user, the following fields are required:

- first_name  
- last_name  
- phone_number  

After the user is inserted into the database, an id is automatically generated and assigned.

---

## Database

- The database used is MySQL  
- All data is stored in the database  
- Each user has a unique id generated automatically

---

## Docker

- The FastAPI server runs in its own Docker container  
- The MySQL database runs in a separate Docker container  
- Port mapping:
  - FastAPI: 8000:8000
  - MySQL: 3306:3306

---

## Usage

1. Clone the project from GitHub  
2. Run the following command:

docker compose up
